text: Raketa Stadium is a sports venue in Kazan.http://www.rusbandy.ru/stadium/9/ It is the home of Dynamo Kazan. == History == * Stadium was built in 1947. * In 2000 the stadium hosted the Russian Government Cup. * Hosted the 2005 and 2011 Bandy World Championships. ==References== Category:Bandy venues in Russia Category:Sport in Kazan
title: Raketa Stadium
